RESEARCH ALERT - Citrix raised . Robertson , Stephens & Company analyst John Powers raised the rating on Citrix Systems Inc from long - term attractive to buy . - - Powers said a licensing deal with Microsoft payment revenues , with recognition over time of a one time $ 75 million lump - sum payment , should not be capitalized , in his view . - - Without the EPS of $ 0 . 32 that represents , his next year ' s estimate is $ 1 . 27 . Cash on the balance sheet of $ 8 per share is a significant factor . - - Powers sees substantial upside to his published $ 1 . 59 for next year but , with a ramp that is still hard to predict , he is not willing to post higher numbers yet . 
